<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282190>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 − 21. Forewings of Hemicaecilius spp. 14, 16, 18 and 20, males. 15, 17, 19 and 21, females. 14 – 15. H. mockfordi n. sp. 16 – 17. H. smithersi n. sp. 18 – 19. H. nicolasi n. sp. 20 – 21. H. rauli n. sp. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282193>
    dc:description "FIGURES 36 – 42. Hemicaecilius rauli n. sp. 36 – 38. Female. 39 – 42. Male. 36. Subgenital plate. 37. Epiproct and paraprocts. 38. Gonapophyses and ninth sternum. 39. Epiproct, paraprocts and clunium. 40. Side view of genitals. 41. Hypandrium and claspers. 42. Phallosome apodemes. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282193/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

